{"msg":{"list":[{"title":null,"userName":"砚","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay1sAUiaeMjXkgTIsWr9YXjAkiaPCPTNOPRn87Ww75nYc6WqkPKSHquVAhKuDPicUX6UicFDxMgXv61Eic/0","content":"<img src=\"http://static.iqycamp.com/application-20170420112255-rtbmkb32o-.jpg\" style=\"max-width:90%\"><br>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8364,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492658588000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"MEI","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay4WSia00Ha3mhXJUGgwjS6ktLlFk1x79xOEjmhD7TTm5ndUeg9M2MBOI7jt4kxhR1BeMVGgyp9ZZH/0","content":"<p><b>主题：多种资源配置方式有助于资产保值增值。</b></p><p><b>论点1：人民币潜在的贬值风险。</b></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">第四季度央行将维持稳健的货币政策，今年内央行再次降息降准是小概率事件。（2016年）9月份CPI同比上涨1.9%，涨幅连续4个月处“1时代”，即便CPI增幅放缓，把钱存在银行的收益依然追不上物价飞涨的速度，也就是说你把钱存在银行相当于赔钱。</span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 28px;\"><b>论点2：境外投资产品分析。&nbsp;</b></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">自2015年初开始，有些敏感的投资者关注到人民币潜在的贬值风险，已经开始主动了解境外的资产的配置。例如，债券类的固定派息的产品以及海外的房产投资，或为自己和家人买一些境外保险。</span><br></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">分支1：外币理财产品。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">数据显示，9月份发行的人民币理财产品平均收益率为3.7%，美元理财产品平均收益率为1.57%，如果算上美元近一年升值6%的优势，即使扣去0.4%的换汇成本，购买美元理财产品比购买人民币理财产品收益率要高。</span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 28px; background-color: transparent;\">海外投资产品中，美元投资类产品门槛较高，一般在15万美元以上，且投资期限较长。除去汇率波动因素，这些产品的预期收益率普遍较国内理财产品低。</span><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">外汇投资类产品投资周期相对较长。例如，股权产品一般是投资期3~4年，加上退出期达4~5年。在投资期之内不排除有项目退出、资金回流的可能性。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">投资美元存款和美元理财有助于资产保值，但如果只是短期持有美元，高昂的手续费可能抵消换汇收益。分析师提醒，外币理财产品依旧较为小众化，对投资者把握外汇走势的能力要求较高，因此建议投资者谨慎购买。</span><br></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">分支2：境外保险。</span><br></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">境外保险产品相对与其他的理财产品而言比较稳妥一点。与中国内地居民而言，配置香港保险无疑是最佳的选择。</span><br></span></p>","voteCount":1,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8355,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492657474000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"乔纳金","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoMyqCnmt2EVaPgbEhVibNCOp2juadCUynibe7Xc7pWmRgydDiaexkbpGmn0iayeBWHwvjNEmicWVEXIrY/0","content":"人民币理财产品收益低与美元境外投资理财投资<div>境外投资理财有风险</div><div>境外投资理财投资预期效果香港保险最佳选择</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8351,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492657050000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Yuly","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6YKhicCzFyyb5ibeAwJJ3mHXbP6ia1YEZoRjiaoFUFvO8VTzSUN6eKSVxFPrQC3IicSPxXdMFDRE99WrX1uOHNL5n3f3/0","content":"1.美元理财产品收益率＞人民币理财产品收益率；<div>2.理财有风险，投资需谨慎；</div><div>3.钱存银行就是赔钱；</div><div>4.境外理财产品投资期周期长；</div><div>5.配置香港保险更合算。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8331,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492654776000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Livi","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6ZdgpcbFicUQFLRcpoJCTFQjK74cBqTCm2qTcpVAAuPDZSl87PcAwZR1TA5p80yGu4FuzXtrPaOpaqkZjjl8JCSg/0","content":"1 美元理财产品vs人民币理财产品，前者完胜<div>2 外币理财产品，小众，能力要求高，慎购</div><div>3 人民币降息，勿存</div><div>4 投资者开始了解境外保险</div><div>5 海外投资产品，美元投资类，门槛高，期限长，收益率低</div><div>6 外汇投资产品周期长</div><div>7 境外保险好</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8317,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492653418000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"虹","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6ibMZWbia4B13kv4I652cNbheF6LpAdL1wiaJWrd3IH1l4rKQJVibLsHzT5pOibfia5rocIqbhUOwiatk1Dp8UUnlHZGBV/0","content":"1.人民币存银行等于赔钱，要进行理财。<div>2.美元理财产品回报率高于人民币理财产品，但投资周期长，风险大，需要谨慎。</div><div>3.人民币贬值，海外投资产品收益率比国内产品低。</div><div>4.外汇类投资产品周期长。</div><div>5.内地居民配置香港保险是最佳选择。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8305,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492652762000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"没想好","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcKVSJ7zgg19tXarFcWEZ707hTQb3eDeTQ5WW2JdCoapbu7yfJygalIL2am4Wx9OiclyFwaMLdOn4EfY8YIYlq2WQ/0","content":"投资美元存款和美元理财有助于资产保值，但如果只是短期持有美元，高昂的手续费可能抵消换汇收益。<div>境外保险产品相对与其他的理财产品而言比较稳妥一点。与中国内地居民而言，配置香港保险无疑是最佳的选择。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8290,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492651316000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"伏大哲","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay2ibB2Bjib5vXuMvxdORfBia7u0py2bG7wgtr8cYvhiabic5wAlDbr0ibkg8OPQamojNSTQILbkIcBdUuB/0","content":"境内资产配置方式。 &nbsp;银行存款 国内理财产品&nbsp;<div>境外资产配置方式。美元存款 美元理财产品 境外房地产 香港保险</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8274,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492649861000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"luyuan\uD83C\uDF80","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ajNVdqHZLLBRhlPuUrO8ic4yPQib6ogmGV3WYgpBXv9IaOyf775RlNlJXRrqJibXWu4WHXXePvfRkygFahv0WtO6A/0","content":"1.第四季度维稳货币政策导致钱存银行相当于赔钱。<div>2.外币理财投资门槛高，需长期投资，风险大。</div><div>3.配置香港保险是最佳选择。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8252,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492647189000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"天边的白云","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ajNVdqHZLLAH3KEpkdUGQ0Qv2JJVpickBk2eslCpIl7pIvkYM47ohTcuDwQUmk0pN41j47PBpGSibJMviaoDQKM4w/0","content":"优化资产配置，抵御资产贬值风险。<div>可考虑海外投资和购置境外保险产品。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8226,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492643293000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"蒋竟红","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/TVwhicV1539IW2Fx75h6RibXbgvj8SXxQOWnQ2NQyiaJpDOoQibSUa31ibq6DnRxXVBE1wib3dZAcU54d3VkqyC0lqhLI8dgwiaWm6L/0","content":"人民币贬值，存银行等于亏钱，美元升值，建议进行境外投资，美元投资和外汇投资风险大，周期长，建议投资境外保险产品，其中香港保险最为理想。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8215,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492641393000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"cxl66","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-19","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6ZaLoY2RXU5FaaP4muNZJkxtwYTJT78ic7yJpy2tfBQw7pkibmRK8UmQOCoPvpIaQjB4hIMMkFDibhnecVbVHkNJYM/0","content":"银行存钱的收益抵不上物价飞涨的速度，存钱等于亏钱，很多人选择投资理财，并把目光放在境外投资。一，海外理财产品，购买美元理财产品会比国内的收益高，但毕竟小众，有风险要谨慎选择。二，海外投资产品，门槛高，期限长，收益低。三，境外保险产品，较理财产品稳妥，国内居民首选香港保险。","voteCount":1,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8180,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492616356000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Richard","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-19","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/gAnTFfFuHAmh0SjuKwCo0n6d4ICaPjSJudvRhBGOg7SicCR7qfsQN2IXlr9V6ZPcFFRiaS8IfZp6fCbYicO0grcARJ3SMYhVciaD/0","content":"<div><span style=\"font-size: 1.6em;\">近年个人海外投资资产配置的最佳选择——香港保险。</span></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 1.6em;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 根据2016年</span><span style=\"font-size: 1.6em;\">第四季度央行将维持稳健的货币政策，CPI的数据分析来看,将钱存入银行的利息是抵不过物价飞涨的，那存入的钱无疑就是赔钱。</span></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 1.6em;\">我们为了减少人民币潜在贬值的风险，可以向境外投资。外汇投资类产品投资周期长，如美元入门栏高，不确定因素多，预期收益普遍较国内理财低。而短期的外币投资，则要个人对于外汇走势能力强。相比之下，</span><span style=\"font-size: 1.6em;\">境外的保险产品较为稳健，无疑是中国国内人民的最佳选择。</span></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 1.6em;\"><br></span></div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8178,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492616262000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"ni_ni","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-19","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay0RTzLMxtdmR2fOMvYiajibIsJC2skOHEsHATYDiclpYX1ZWSiaSlPYFoFthSQF6PDWVHxcicmH2K10M1/0","content":"<p>目前投资环境来看，配置香港保险是目前投资的最佳选择。原因有二：</p><p>第一，国内市场人民币有贬值倾向，存银行是贬值的。</p><p>第二，<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">外币理财小众化，风险高，</span>外汇投资类产品投资周期相对较长，美元投资门槛高。</p><p>因此，境外保险产品相对稳妥，是最佳选择。</p>","voteCount":1,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8176,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492616209000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"云烨","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-19","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ajNVdqHZLLBnmFdUOSKO7NoOWG57ADLBUSpKggjHL1rgIFMU9DwFEOUdf94pY7ohlhRxvuQNoMpVsrz1UqicE0g/0","content":"把钱存在银行等同于赔钱，所以目前应该选择一种理财方式，以进行资产的保值或增值。<div>投资美元存款和美元理财有助于资产保值。虽然美元理财产品的预期收益率普遍低于国内理财产品，但考虑到汇率变动，若长期持有，其综合收益率还是由为可观。</div><div>此外，配置海外资产也是一种不错的选择，特别是配置香港保险尤其适合国内居民。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8165,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492615234000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"koala","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-19","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcKAWnG9iaqcwGupCK0wSLTmYnFZHWOHEB5ElpiaYUjCQZH349nkkibWsPd5nbS06y6GcnlLibKyoDmTZaRF5tl3y3zj/0","content":"当前人民币贬值，钱存在银行相当于赔钱。购买美元理财产品是个不错的选择。美元理财产品比人民币理财产品实际收益率高，更有利于资产保值。但美元理财产品对投资者能力要求高，资金门槛高，手续费高，投资周期长，预期收益普遍低于国内。建议购买香港保险产品比较稳妥。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8163,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492615154000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Bertha","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-19","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AyzSHkKJ0Ll6HEqZl1AIuAR77FIHvwJwN3mYBicYPEibRxagoHAkWCuxKXWI4ZpZKXhjSfpqGqMHwM2/0","content":"1.银行理财（没有升值空间）<div>2.美元理财（不建议短期，税率较高）<div>3.外汇理财（周期长，不稳定）</div><div>4.外境保险产品（比较稳妥）</div></div>","voteCount":1,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8160,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492614925000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"圣光","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-19","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98UznyebbicsTfdAJT7mXpRJQMQbNricOUmnbrckT5vBy1XDSveR8icrFo4T3pYt8uh4Zwe75VGVz1ic1K2sCPdjXDZh/0","content":"结论:进行境外的资产配置，有助于抵御人民币贬值的风险。<div>1.美元投资类产品门槛高，周期长，收益率比国内理财产品低，</div><div>2.外汇投资类产品周期长，风险大。</div><div>3.境外保险产品相对稳妥，建议配备香港保险。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8113,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492612349000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"你把天聊死了~","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-19","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pQbpZsHIXiar9uAyrMRypBMwwO9KK4QmBcR5kxYibk1otH6nHm4YTy2k3qCK1CGgkibibFoJZErwjD2BkSBo5tlSj1A58Ah40m3s/0","content":"高风险投资，存钱到银行，买美国短期理财产品<div>保值投资，买长期境外产品，买香港保险产品</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8108,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492611897000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"ing","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-19","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6icIK0BaTrZAQHDpGibvP5EYq90TgaQjYZ9Z3iaZDOqFEOhKNDAiaZx8tFO8YPJmgYTS22kkC6uaOTyUnticmYd2LFxX/0","content":"从所有咨询中可以了解到，收益的高低，风险大小，在分析的同时也权衡了利与弊","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8084,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492611139000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]}],"highlightList":[],"end":false},"code":200}
